

What it can do
------------------
- Can be used to test any input & output format unlike MRUnit
- Local Job Runner is set using mapreduce.framework.name=local
- Entire MapReduce Engine runs in a single JVM
- Can also be used to access HDFS(Apart from Local File system)

De-merits
----------
- Not possible to test Partitioners(Multiple Reducers) because of single JVM

What Next
------------
- Mini MR Cluster


Reference
--------------

H.D.Guide : Page 157
P.A.Hadoop : Page 173
 
